<title type="html"><![CDATA[Después de 2666 días de espera, sale SDL 2.0]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://losersjuegos.com.ar/foro/viewtopic.php?t=3029&amp;p=9266#p9266"><![CDATA[
Hola! Hace bastante que no ando por acá y bueno quería compartir esta noticia que seguro a alguno le interesa:<br /><a href="http://forums.libsdl.org/viewtopic.php?p=38569&amp;sid=9efbea827cdebd71ee430cda823bcdc7#38569" class="postlink">http://forums.libsdl.org/viewtopic.php?p=38569&amp;sid=9efbea827cdebd71ee430cda823bcdc7#38569</a><br /><span style="text-decoration: underline">Descarga</span>: <a href="http://www.libsdl.org/download-2.0.php" class="postlink">http://www.libsdl.org/download-2.0.php</a><br /><span style="text-decoration: underline">Cambios/Mejoras:</span><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br />Full 3D hardware acceleration <br />Support for OpenGL 3.0+ in various profiles (core, compatibility, debug, robust, etc) <br />Support for OpenGL ES <br />Support for multiple windows <br />Support for multiple displays <br />Support for multiple audio devices <br />Android and iOS support <br />Simple 2D rendering API that can use Direct3D, OpenGL, OpenGL ES, or software rendering behind the scenes <br />Force Feedback available on Windows, Mac OS X and Linux <br />XInput and XAudio2 support for Windows <br />Atomic operations <br />Power management (exposes battery life remaining, etc) <br />Shaped windows <br />32-bit audio (int and float) <br />Simplified Game Controller API (the Joystick API is still here, too!) <br />Touch support (multitouch, gestures, etc) <br />Better fullscreen support <br />Better keyboard support (scancodes vs keycodes, etc). <br />Message boxes <br />Clipboard support <br />Basic Drag'n'Drop support <br />Proper unicode input and IME support <br />A really powerful assert macro <br />Lots of old annoyances from 1.2 are gone <br />Many other things!<br /></div></blockquote><br />Habrá que probar y ver!  <img src="http://losersjuegos.com.ar/foro/images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" /> <br />Saludos!<p>Estadísticas: Publicado por <a href="http://losersjuegos.com.ar/foro/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2393">ClRg</a> — Jue Ago 15, 2013 12:46 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
